yom kiper UNK iz zi geshtorbn ⟨oyf⟩ a rak.

00:10:52.652 --> 00:10:54.890
mayn shvoger iz ersht VORIGES yor geshtorbn.

00:10:55.082 --> 00:10:57.151
⟨di⟩ tsvey zun kumt tsu mir ⟨aroyf⟩.

00:10:58.879 --> 00:11:03.564
un ale sh- i- andere shvesters iz umgekumen?

00:11:02.132 --> 00:11:03.475
ales iz umgekumen

00:11:03.891 --> 00:11:06.382
du bist geblibn nor mit di eyne shvester?

00:11:05.005 --> 00:11:06.392
ikh bin, yo, yo.

00:11:07.705 --> 00:11:08.323
yo.

00:11:08.785 --> 00:11:11.310
zi iz geven far mir ⟨do⟩ vi a, vi a muter.

00:11:12.447 --> 00:11:15.563
az dayn JULIA iz geven a kind.

00:11:16.058 --> 00:11:17.674
du host ir fartseylt?

00:11:17.674 --> 00:11:19.848
fun GETO LODZH un fun ales?

00:11:18.825 --> 00:11:22.780
UNK zi veyst ales UNK ikh bin a, zi hot gevoynt.

00:11:23.770 --> 00:11:25.080
gehat oyf di

00:11:25.103 --> 00:11:27.358
TOCHNIT LAMED hot zi gehat a voynung

00:11:27.820 --> 00:11:33.349
iz dos yingl tsu ir gekumen, zogt er "OMA, dertseyl mir vi s'iz gevezn," zogt ikh "freg dayn mame. efsher vil zi nisht."

00:11:34.097 --> 00:11:37.533
zog ikh "JULIA, zol ikh fartseyln?" zogt zi yo, hob ikh im ales fartseylt oykhet.

00:11:37.658 --> 00:11:39.238
er hot dos ales farshtanen.

00:11:41.305 --> 00:11:43.265
nu, shoyn, dos iz geven di gantse.

00:11:42.250 --> 00:11:43.223
un

00:11:43.223 --> 00:11:45.400
bay nakht gedenkstu zakhn?

00:11:45.070 --> 00:11:47.210
nu UNK

00:11:46.013 --> 00:11:47.303
vos gedenkstu?

00:11:47.210 --> 00:11:51.219
az ikh geb mikh a khap oyf, geyt UNK a dos, a dos UNK

00:11:51.259 --> 00:11:53.095
UNK ikh nem ⟨es⟩ tsu shlofn.

00:11:53.095 --> 00:11:54.442
shlof ikh shoyn ⟨in geto⟩.

00:11:54.583 --> 00:11:58.087
ober vo- dos, ⟨hot dos⟩ eyns aleyn tsu zayn

00:11:58.380 --> 00:12:00.719
dos iz ⟨dos⟩ ergste vos GIBT oyf di velt.

00:12:02.228 --> 00:12:04.376
ikh kum aheym in di shtub arayn. s'iz nokh f-

00:12:04.376 --> 00:12:06.423
nokh nakht, a halb nayn.

00:12:06.852 --> 00:12:08.989
zits ikh shpetsyel biz tsveleve

00:12:09.417 --> 00:12:13.056
kh'zol lenger zitsn. tsi es gefelt mir, tsi es gefelt mir nisht, zits ikh.

00:12:13.568 --> 00:12:15.570
nem ikh UNK, gey ikh shlofn

00:12:15.677 --> 00:12:19.113
vakh oyf in di fri, bin ikh nervez, vayl ikh ze s'iz keyner nishto

00:12:20.453 --> 00:12:22.691
un azoy geyt dos lebn. s'iz zeyer biter.

00:12:22.719 --> 00:12:25.273
di tokhter, di tokhter voynt in Vin.

00:12:24.739 --> 00:12:29.157
yo. zey hobn zeyer gevolt ikh zol voynen. zey hobn mikh gehat HERLICH EINGERICHTET dort

00:12:29.157 --> 00:12:32.918
BEEMET UNK e- dos hot mayn ey- eydem gehat dos far ⟨zikh⟩.

00:12:32.586 --> 00:12:35.567
der eydem iz a ts- tseyn dokter, yo?

00:12:35.100 --> 00:12:36.866
yo. er iz do geboyrn.

00:12:37.108 --> 00:12:38.131
in Yisroel.

00:12:38.143 --> 00:12:43.374
er iz a g- bakanter tseyn dokter, un er makht WIRKLICH GUT gelt, un zi arbet

00:12:43.374 --> 00:12:44.966
WUNDERBAR mit dermit

00:12:46.761 --> 00:12:52.251
ober ikh hob nisht gekent dort lebn. far vos? n- dos ⟨vos zey⟩ arbetn hot mikh nisht geshtert

00:12:52.251 --> 00:12:55.221
ober zenen yunge mentshn. ikh shter zeyer lebn

00:12:55.283 --> 00:13:00.711
⟨az⟩ avekforn, un ikh ken nisht aleynt blaybn in a voynung mit zibn tsimern aleyn tsu voynen.

00:13:02.202 --> 00:13:04.001
ober m'hot gedarft UNK forn

00:13:04.058 --> 00:13:06.459
nokh UNK zumer nokh ISRAEL

00:13:06.459 --> 00:13:09.891
UNK zumer, hob ikh nisht gevolt tsurikforn, bin ikh geblibn do.

00:13:10.572 --> 00:13:13.603
UNK geven, ikh bin geven, s'hot mir fun gornisht gefelt.

00:13:13.980 --> 00:13:17.588
zey hobn ⟨geshtert⟩. er hot mikh shlekht gefilt, hot er bald ongeklungen

00:13:17.588 --> 00:13:20.505
UNK "Khave, gey aroyf. di mame filt zikh nisht gut."

00:13:21.996 --> 00:13:23.781
UNK ⟨UND⟩ er hot shoyn geshikt ales

00:13:23.781 --> 00:13:28.706
zenen geven WUNDERBAR UNK. dos vos zeyer gantse yorn le- hobn nisht lib tsu esn

00:13:28.982 --> 00:13:33.228
UNK zey hobn gevust ikh hob es lib, hobn zikh tsugeveynt tsu dem.

00:13:33.420 --> 00:13:34.520
iz zey hobn ges- s-

00:13:34.520 --> 00:13:36.328
ikh ken gornisht ⟨mir⟩ zogn keyn ⟨shlekhtes⟩.

00:13:36.328 --> 00:13:37.582
k- absolut nisht.

00:13:38.483 --> 00:13:40.480
un di kinder zenen gevezn. zey hobn

00:13:40.480 --> 00:13:43.540
far a por monat iz gevezn, iz geven zeyer heys.

00:13:43.540 --> 00:13:46.273
hot ⟨zayn⟩ shvester di t- tokhter gemakht a khasene

00:13:46.802 --> 00:13:48.990
zenen zey gekumen ⟨oykh⟩ ale ⟨dort⟩.

00:13:49.384 --> 00:13:52.348
yetst, azoy hot mikh mayn tokhter makht UNK

00:13:52.455 --> 00:13:53.681
seyder

00:13:53.957 --> 00:13:57.287
un v- ver s'hot, ruft on, kum aroyf.

00:13:57.287 --> 00:13:58.204
kum aroyf.

00:13:58.783 --> 00:14:01.595
⟨hobn zey gezogt eyn mol⟩ UNK kum do aher.

00:14:01.838 --> 00:14:03.924
me geyt mir UNK

00:14:05.905 --> 00:14:07.859
un du gedenkst zakhn

00:14:07.859 --> 00:14:11.248
ale mol in, bay nakht gedenkstu?

00:14:09.870 --> 00:14:12.429
nisht bloyz bay nakht. ikh zits aleynt.

00:14:12.621 --> 00:14:18.639
vet mir keyn ⟨gutes⟩ NIE KOMMEN in kop arayn. ale idyotishe zakhn, ale, alerley shlekhte zakhn GIBN mir DAMALS in kop.

00:14:21.953 --> 00:14:26.723
dos, dos ken men nisht aroys. fun dem ken men nisht fargesn. me tor nisht redn azoy fil me redt nisht

00:14:26.723 --> 00:14:29.403
ober vos vest nisht redn UNK kumst oyf dem teme.

00:14:34.153 --> 00:14:36.492
vos vilstu zogn far di eyniklekh?

00:14:37.562 --> 00:14:39.294
zey zoln mir zayn gezunt

00:14:41.275 --> 00:14:43.065
un zoln nisht fargesn az zey hobn a bobe.

00:14:43.065 --> 00:14:45.775
a OMA. dos iz OMA dort.

00:14:46.050 --> 00:14:46.769
yo?

00:14:47.130 --> 00:14:50.729
ikh ⟨vel zey⟩ nokh l- iberlozn, UNK ⟨ikh vel⟩ shtarbn, vil ikh UNK

00:14:50.729 --> 00:14:54.307
UNK ikh hob ⟨DAMALS ven⟩ mayn man iz geshorbn, UNK nisht ⟨farshteyn⟩

00:14:54.307 --> 00:14:57.114
kh'hob nisht gevust az me hot gekoyft a ts- a keyver

00:14:58.183 --> 00:15:00.320
ikh hob ⟨aleyn⟩ keyn anung nisht gehat.

00:15:01.153 --> 00:15:03.627
zoln zey koyfn un dort mikh bagrobn.

00:15:04.292 --> 00:15:06.345
akhibe zey veln mikh nemen UNK

00:15:07.549 --> 00:15:10.023
oyfhengen veln zey mikh nisht UNK

00:15:10.755 --> 00:15:13.702
zenen gute kinder, ober zey hobn zeyer lebn.

00:15:12.726 --> 00:15:16.031
zey, zey, zey bakumen a yidishn CHINUCH?

00:15:16.138 --> 00:15:17.245
di kinder?

00:15:16.746 --> 00:15:17.890
yo.

00:15:17.890 --> 00:15:22.241
er hot gemakht d- m'hot gemakht a bar mitsve far dem yingl, gevezn UNK opgemakht.

00:15:22.956 --> 00:15:25.970
gekumen a lerer, hot gelernt, un yetst di kleyne lernt.

00:15:24.981 --> 00:15:27.371
zey visn az zey zenen yidn.

00:15:26.871 --> 00:15:28.552
z- umbadingt

00:15:28.710 --> 00:15:32.011
zi arbet bay di, tsum bayshpil bay di AL e- EL AL, yo?

00:15:32.338 --> 00:15:33.277
iz shoyn

00:15:33.300 --> 00:15:34.571
⟨oys⟩geshlosn.

00:15:34.571 --> 00:15:38.191
vayl der firer iz mayn khaver oykhet oyfgeshlosn ⟨iz dos bay dos⟩

00:15:38.191 --> 00:15:41.766
UND dos yingl arbet bay di yidishe gemeynde, iz dokh ⟨er⟩ geshlosn.

00:15:42.328 --> 00:15:44.617
z- er geyt in shul arayn azoy

00:15:44.893 --> 00:15:50.523
zey zenen nisht keyn frume mentshn, ober zey zenen yidishe mentshn, mit a gut UNK mit a gut harts

00:15:51.323 --> 00:15:55.773
az undz hot men dort gevoynt, ver s'iz geven gekumen fun ISRAEL hot men gemuzt shtayer

00:15:55.773 --> 00:15:57.603
⟨bashtayer in kantselarye geyn⟩

00:15:57.603 --> 00:16:01.293
yetst kumt tsu zey UNK. er hot gearbet ⟨do⟩ in shpitol m- bay ⟨mer⟩

00:16:01.293 --> 00:16:04.800
zenen fun UNK a sakh GEKOMMEN, er hot nokh do zeyer gute CHAVERIM.

00:16:06.460 --> 00:16:09.744
iz dos vilstu zogn far di eyniklekh, zoln zey zayn gezunt?

00:16:09.244 --> 00:16:12.360
zey zoln zayn gezunt un zoln nisht fargesn zey hobn a OMA.

00:16:13.817 --> 00:16:14.823
dos iz dos.

00:16:16.028 --> 00:16:19.447
UNK zol zayn gezunt.

00:16:21.681 --> 00:16:23.767
TODA RABA, GEVERET SZTAIER

00:16:22.997 --> 00:16:24.121
TODA RABA

00:16:24.212 --> 00:16:25.893
zol nisht fargesn keyner.

00:16:26.507 --> 00:16:30.703
bruder yi- d- der tsveyter, heyst er Zelik mit zayn froy.

00:16:30.996 --> 00:16:33.504
in velkhn yor ho- m'hot gemakht dem bild?

00:16:33.544 --> 00:16:35.310
d- far, far dem krig.

00:16:35.316 --> 00:16:36.508
far dem krig.

00:16:37.071 --> 00:16:38.162
-ayn man

00:16:38.522 --> 00:16:40.476
mayn tokhter's VA- foter

00:16:40.476 --> 00:16:41.806
JAKUB SZTAIER

00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:44.794
dos iz a bild UNK

00:16:45.964 --> 00:16:49.859
dos iz a bil vos UNK mayn tsveyt UNK tsveyter man

00:16:49.859 --> 00:16:51.763
Tsvi LEVINGER

00:16:52.866 --> 00:16:54.784
mayn nomen v- veyst ets.

00:16:56.443 --> 00:17:00.065
ot dem bild zey men di UNK vos ma- mayn UNK

00:17:01.438 --> 00:17:04.638
eynikl MIK- MICHAEL RAUCHMANN

00:17:05.640 --> 00:17:08.435
SEINE muter, JULIA RAUCHMANN

00:17:09.285 --> 00:17:11.624
SEINE shvester, DORIT

00:17:12.087 --> 00:17:14.021
⟨un⟩ mayn, d-

00:17:14.230 --> 00:17:15.880
d- dem, der foter

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:19.252
RAPHAEL RAUCHMANN. DOKTOR UNK RAUCHMANN.

00:17:19.306 --> 00:17:22.275
z- zogt zey, dos iz mayn tokhter

00:17:22.275 --> 00:17:24.240
mit di kinder. zog.

00:17:22.370 --> 00:17:26.019
yo, yo. dos iz, dos iz mayn tokhter mit di kinder mitn man.

00:17:26.733 --> 00:17:28.655
un ikh vintsh zey ale, ALLES GUTES.
